      "narrative": "A readily identifiable employee or attendant was not present during periods of public contact with animals. The\nwalkthrough \u201cBudgie Adventure Aviary\u201d was found to have no attendants present while members of the public interacted\nand feed the budgies within. Without an attendant present to monitor these interaction, both animals and members of the\npublic are placed at an increased risk of injury. The facility must have a responsible, knowledgeable, and readily\nidentifiable employee or attendant present at all times during periods of public contact. Corrected at the time of inspection\non April 27, 2026.\nThis inspection and exit interview were conducted with facility representatives.\nn"
    }
